    "description": "We at Asian Paints Signature Store Consulting Pvt Ltd are looking for an experienced Floor Manager based out of Agra. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Asian Paints Signature Store Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nAsian Paints Signature Store Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Customer Service\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Referral bonus program\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Agra, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Asian Paints Signature Store Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
